96.6723, 294.4819, 295.8708, 297.8508, 297.9425, 298.6675, 300.4277, 298.1318, 298.9529, 300.9144, 301.7538, 300.7127, 302.4303, 300.4444, 301.6381, 301.3014, 302.0658, 298.5463, 294.8335, 296.1957, 296.8501, 295.0953, 295.5004, 296.8539, 297.319, 296.9616, 295.6414, 296.2697, 296.9146, 296.7152, 296.9674, 298.6264, 301.6588, 306.6971, 305.3632, 307.7063, 309.8434, 310.0804, 306.99, 307.4593, 307.6146, 307.3039, 310.3986, 309.9931, 315.7611, 318.4986, 316.5684, 314.7501, 315.9132, 312.0931, 315.6652, 316.0788, 314.2874, 314.1355, 311.3998, 317.2141, 318.1613, 319.0436, 313.2103, 315.1259, 312.3504, 312.783, 312.3314, 311.8525, 310.9384, 310.4347, 309.8385, 310.8916, 311.0734, 311.0363, 311.1141, 311.5578, 312.439, 312.2749, 312.1765, 310.1958, 308.5669, 307.5487, 306.7538, 307.0446, 307.0521, 306.857, 306.3579, 307.0217, 306.8866, 307.326, 307.6126, 307.8549, 310.1239, 308.8615, 309.311, 308.613, 309.2168, 309.6736, 309.3215, 309.9947, 310.412, 311.9178, 312.3344, 311.4413, 312.2622, 312.0669, 311.6384, 311.3552, 310.9115, 311.1136], "summary_html": "<h1>Volatility-Momentum Interaction Factor</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>来源研报《Information Content of Return Volatility》(2019,加密货币波动率信息含量),核心思想是收益波动的持续性/长记忆蕴含方向信息。<strong>跨资产迁移到商品期货截面</strong>：用 GARCH(1,1) 条件波动率的变化率刻画\"波动持续性变化\",再用 20日价格动量符号给出方向,二者交互——<strong>波动率放大趋势方向上的动量信号</strong>。</p>\n<p><strong>实盘变体 <code>vol_mom_h10_raw</code>,信号构造严格按 <code>strategy_final.py</code></strong>： 1. per sym 对数收益 <code>lr</code>(先按 polars 口径丢掉每个品种首行 prev_close 缺失行,保证 GARCH 索引对齐)。 2. 暖机门控字段(仅用于过滤,不进信号)：已实现波动率 <code>rvol_60</code>(60日,年化)、EWMA 波动率 <code>ewma_vol</code>(λ=0.94)、跳跃频率 <code>jump_freq</code>(60日,|lr|/rvol·√252 &gt; 3 的占比)。<strong>无 Hurst 指数</strong>。 3. GARCH(1,1) Zero-mean 条件波动率 <code>cond_vol</code>(窗口252,每20日重拟合,min_obs=120,<code>arch_model</code> 并行8进程内联计算,非预算 parquet)。 4. 波动持续性变化率：<code>vol_persist_chg = cond_vol(t)/cond_vol(t-20) - 1</code>(仅 cond_vol 滞后值 &gt;0 且有限时有效)。 5. 20日动量符号：<code>sign(close(t)/close(t-20) - 1)</code>(动量缺失/为零时符号取0)。 6. 交互信号：<code>vol_mom_interact = vol_persist_chg.fillna(0) * sign(mom_20)</code>。 7. 丢弃暖机行(rvol_60/ewma_vol/jump_freq 任一缺失) → 截面 rank → 连续信号 → <code>vol_target_scale(15%, 60日)</code> → <strong><code>rebalance_hold(10日)</code></strong>(<code>cs_factor_to_position</code> 一次完成)。</p>\n<p><strong>做多/做空方向</strong>：波动持续性上升(vol_persist_chg&gt;0)且动量向上→做多,波动上升但动量向下→做空;即在波动放大时顺势放大动量方向暴露。<strong>关键发现</strong>：方向与原报告波动持续性思路一致;全期 Sharpe 约 1.12(扣4bps),样本内(2016-2025)0.97,变体为 <code>_raw</code> 归一化、hold=10。<strong>防前视</strong>：cond_vol/动量均用正向 <code>shift(20)</code>,<code>rebalance_hold</code> ffill 因果,审计判定无前视。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.54</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>6.3%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.1%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-4.6%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.11</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3368</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.65</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>1.22</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.68 / 1.63</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.48</td><td>1.82</td><td>1.37</td><td>1.52</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.02</span></td><td>1.89</td><td>0.22</td><td>0.28</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.73</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.25</span></td><td>1.61</td><td>0.92</td><td>1.54</td><td>1.49</td><td>0.89</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>open</code></td><td>开盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>high</code></td><td>最高价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>low</code></td><td>最低价</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 10 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 10 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3370</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>98.2%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>40.8</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{vol\\_persist\\_chg}_t = \\frac{\\sigma^{GARCH}_t}{\\sigma^{GARCH}_{t-20}} - 1</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{vol\\_mom\\_interact}_t = \\text{vol\\_persist\\_chg}_t \\times \\text{sign}\\!\\big(\\tfrac{P_t}{P_{t-20}} - 1\\big)</div>\n<p>截面 rank → 连续信号 → vol_target_scale(15%) → rebalance_hold(<strong>10日</strong>)。</p>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>RVOL_WINDOW</code></td><td><code>60</code></td><td>warm-up gate: realized vol</td></tr><tr><td><code>EWMA_LAMBDA</code></td><td><code>0.94</code></td><td>warm-up gate: EWMA vol</td></tr><tr><td><code>JUMP_THRESHOLD</code></td><td><code>3.0</code></td><td>warm-up gate: jump detection</td></tr><tr><td><code>JUMP_FREQ_WINDOW</code></td><td><code>60</code></td><td>warm-up gate: jump-freq rolling window</td></tr><tr><td><code>MOM_WINDOW</code></td><td><code>20</code></td><td>momentum lookback</td></tr><tr><td><code>VOL_PERSIST_SHIFT</code></td><td><code>20</code></td><td>cond_vol change-rate lookback</td></tr><tr><td><code>HOLD_DAYS</code></td><td><code>10</code></td><td>h10 variant</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 13.85s</li>\n</ul>"}